It seems that Spain's favourite style icon has been taking note of the SS14 catwalks.

Queen Letizia, who is yet to make a fashion faux pas, stepped out for today's royal engagement embracing the season's hottest colours: yellow and white.

The Spanish monarch looked chic and stylish as she and husband King Felipe delivered scholarships at Iberdrola Foundation at Casa America in Madrid.

