Showing a glimpse of a fashion wild side, the 41-year-old accessorised with snakeskin stilettos - a design she's been favouring in recent weeks.

The all-white look is here to stay if 3.1 Phillip Lim and Prabal Gurung's offerings were anything to go by this season. The look has been updated with clever tailoring, clean silhouettes and feminine accents to give it the most minimal effect and the Queen of Spain seems to have nailed the look.

